descriptionHtml:
----------------
Description
AH1 Piercings conversion for SevenBase-MoreBounceBBP.

----------------
Install
Unpack in your skyrim/data folder.

---------------
Uninstall
Delete AH1 Piercing.bsa/bsl/esp

--------------
--------------
All items found in a barrel to the right of the entrance to Dragonsreach (Whiterun Castle). Barrel is named AH1 container.
All items enchantable as jewelry (not craftable). The barrel contains 3 of each item, but if you want more, help AH1 in console will produce the full list.

File contains:

Nipple = biped slot 60 (uses same slots as SED7 Accessoire here: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/20655 )
